Profile management

Usage:
  profile <COMMAND>

Commands:
  list    List all profiles
  create  Create a new profile
  use     Set the active profile
  show    Show profile configuration
  delete  Delete a profile and its stored configuration and credentials
  rename  Rename a profile

Options:
  -h, --help  Print help
